WEBVTT

02:19:37.358 --> 02:19:39.149
Georgekutty buried the body
in his backyard.

02:19:40.566 --> 02:19:41.899
That's how the story should go.

02:19:42.191 --> 02:19:43.191
No.

02:19:44.024 --> 02:19:46.399
We don't need to play games
that cost a life.

02:19:47.524 --> 02:19:49.108
His daughter must go to jail.

02:19:49.608 --> 02:19:52.233
Georgekutty and his family
must feel that agony.
